trans-unit.source: Serves as a repository for information about the views supported by the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeActivityDesigner" /> or classes that inherit from it.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.CompositeActivityDesigner" /> 또는 상속된 클래스에서 지원하는 뷰에 대한 정보의 리포지토리 역할을 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView" /> class.
The integer identifier for the designer view.
The string that specifies the name of the designer view.
The <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Image" /> associated with the designer view.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView" /> class by using an integer, a string, and an <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Image" />.
trans-unit.target: 정수, 문자열 및 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView" />를 사용하여 <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Image" /> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="viewId" /> or <paramref name="text" /> contains <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="viewId" /> 또는 <paramref name="text" />에 <see langword="null" />이 포함된 경우

trans-unit.source: The integer identifier for the designer view.
The string that specifies the name of the designer view.
The <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Image" /> associated with the designer view.
The <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner" /> associated with the designer view.

Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView" /> class by using an integer, a string, an <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Image" />, and an <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner" />.
trans-unit.target: 정수, 문자열, <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView" /> 및 <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Image" />를 사용하여 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner" /> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="viewId" />, <paramref name="text" />, or <paramref name="associatedDesigner" /> contains <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="viewId" />, <paramref name="text" /> 또는 <paramref name="associatedDesigner" />에 <see langword="null" />이 포함된 경우

trans-unit.source: Gets the activity designer associated with the designer view.
trans-unit.target: 디자이너 뷰와 연결된 활동 이미지를 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner" /> associated with the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView" />.
An <see cref="T:System.Object" /> to compare to the current <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView" />.
Determines whether the specified <see cref="T:System.Object" /> is equal to the current designer view.
trans-unit.target: 지정한 <see cref="T:System.Object" />가 현재 디자이너 뷰와 같은지 여부를 확인합니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="obj" /> and the current <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView" /> are equal; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" />와 현재 <paramref name="obj" />가 같으면 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView.Equals%2A> uses the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView.ViewId%2A> property to determine whether the compared designer views are equal.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView.Equals%2A>은 <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView.ViewId%2A> 속성을 사용하여 비교한 디자이너 뷰가 같은지 여부를 확인합니다.

trans-unit.source: Serves as a hash function for the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView" /> and is suitable for use in hashing algorithms and data structures like a hash table.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView" />의 해시 함수 역할을 하고, 해시 알고리즘 및 해시 테이블과 같은 데이터 구조에 사용하기 적합합니다.

trans-unit.source: A hash code for the current <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView" />.
Gets the image associated with the designer view.
The <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Image" /> associated with the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView" />.
Notifies the designer when the view is activated.

<xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView.OnActivate%2A> has no default behavior; classes that inherit from <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView> must implement their own logic.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView.OnActivate%2A>에 기본 동작이 없습니다. <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView>에서 상속된 클래스는 자체적으로 논리를 구현해야 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Notifies the designer when the view is deactivated.

<xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView.OnDeactivate%2A> has no default behavior; classes that inherit from <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView> must implement their own logic.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView.OnDeactivate%2A>에 기본 동작이 없습니다. <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView>에서 상속된 클래스는 자체적으로 논리를 구현해야 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the designer view.
A string that contains the name of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView" />.
Gets the dictionary of user data associated with the designer view.
trans-unit.target: 디자이너 뷰와 연결된 사용자 데이터의 사전을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IDictionary" /> that contains the user data associated with the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Collections.IDictionary" />와 연결된 사용자 데이터가 들어 있는 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView.UserData%2A> is `null`, a <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.HybridDictionary> is created to hold the user data.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView.UserData%2A>가 `null`인 경우에는 사용자 데이터를 저장하기 위해 <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.HybridDictionary>가 생성됩니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the identifier associated with the designer view.
An integer that contains the identifier for the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerView" />.
This property uniquely identifies a view associated with the designer.
trans-unit.target: 이 속성은 디자이너와 연결된 뷰를 고유하게 식별합니다.

trans-unit.source: This property must contain a unique value.
trans-unit.target: 이 속성에는 고유 값이 포함되어야 합니다.
